sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / CI Pipeline
    participant CLI as odh-cli<br/>(kubectl-odh)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant OLM as OLM API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant FS as Local Filesystem

    Note over User,FS: Flow 1: Lint / Upgrade Readiness Assessment

    User->>CLI: kubectl odh lint --target-version 3.4<br/>--checks "components/*" --output table
    CLI->>K8sAPI: GET DataScienceCluster (singleton)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: DSC resource (version, component states)
    CLI->>K8sAPI: GET DSCInitialization (singleton)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: DSCI resource (ServiceMesh config, phase)
    CLI->>K8sAPI: LIST Notebooks (all namespaces)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: Notebook resources
    CLI->>K8sAPI: LIST InferenceServices (all namespaces)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: InferenceService resources
    CLI->>K8sAPI: LIST Subscriptions (OLM operators)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: Subscription resources
    CLI->>K8sAPI: GET ClusterVersion<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: OpenShift version
    Note over CLI: Execute 37 checks:<br/>2 platform, 13 component,<br/>3 dependency, 19 workload
    CLI-->>User: Diagnostic report<br/>(table/json/yaml)

    Note over User,FS: Flow 2: Workload Backup

    User->>CLI: kubectl odh backup --output-dir ./backup<br/>--includes notebooks,inferenceservices
    CLI->>K8sAPI: LIST Notebooks (all namespaces)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: Notebook resources
    CLI->>K8sAPI: LIST InferenceServices (all namespaces)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: InferenceService resources
    Note over CLI: Dependency Resolution:<br/>Chase ConfigMaps, Secrets, PVCs
    CLI->>K8sAPI: GET ConfigMaps (referenced)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: ConfigMap resources
    CLI->>K8sAPI: GET Secrets (referenced)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: Secret resources
    CLI->>K8sAPI: GET PVCs (referenced)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: PVC resources
    Note over CLI: Strip cluster-specific metadata
    CLI->>FS: Write YAML files<br/>(workloads + dependencies)
    CLI-->>User: Backup summary

    Note over User,FS: Flow 3: Kueue Migration (RHBOK)

    User->>CLI: kubectl odh migrate -m kueue-rhbok<br/>--yes
    CLI->>K8sAPI: GET DataScienceCluster<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: DSC (Kueue managementState)
    CLI->>K8sAPI: LIST ClusterQueues, LocalQueues<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: Kueue resources (pre-check)
    CLI->>OLM: CREATE Subscription (kueue-operator)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    OLM-->>CLI: Subscription created
    CLI->>K8sAPI: PATCH DSC (Kueue → Unmanaged)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: DSC updated
    CLI->>K8sAPI: LIST ClusterQueues, LocalQueues<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: Kueue resources (verify integrity)
    CLI-->>User: Migration result
